title: The Fall of the Commonwealth | The Walking Dead Season 11 Theory
author: Reel Talk
description:
How Daryl Will Disrupt the Commonwealth by accidentally being richer than he should be based off his history and standing in their society. Basically, is it possible that that hundred dollar bill will come into play later in the season? It seemed like the Commonwealth was fearful of having single dollars brought into their system... let alone a hundred dollar bill. Is it possible that Daryl could accidentally be one of the richest men in this society? Let's discuss!
